    All Implemented Interfaces:

    public final class OracleClassifier<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Classifier<T>
    A classifier that knows the results perfectly as it receives the gold standard during creation.

    This classifier is used for evaluation if you want to evaluate the effectiveness of CandidateSelection or Clustering without worrying about your Classifier.
